snippet.title: ∞Lena Dunham, Sia, Amber Heard, More Stars Protest Migrant Children Crisis in Texas
snippet.description:
∞Lena Dunham, Sia, Amber Heard, More Stars Protest Migrant Children Crisis in Texas 
Stars including Lena Dunham, Sia, Amber Heard and Joshua Jackson flew to Texas to protest the migrant child crisis that has seen more than 2,300 minors separated from their parents at the U.S./Mexico border. Reese Witherspoon, Chrissy Teigen and More Celebs Speak Out About Migrant Children Crisis Dunham shared a photo of the celebrity group on Instagram, showing them holding signs that said #KeepFamiliesTogether and “End Family Separation.” “We came to Tornillo, Texas, to show our solidarity wit...
